實我自己都幫唔到乜嘢手，走上前面幾個巴打先係真漢子<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0b6436a28606a2c28c56f0ea15efcc030252f71","tid":862384,"uid":109462,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"8535a27c0abdde73843ad41bdb5d83125a671298","tid":862384,"uid":145847,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T19:36:37.000Z","msg":"口罩又唔比帶,野又唔講<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xS9a3tr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxS9a3tr.jpg&h=e0ec3a76&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T19:37:36.000Z","msg":"已經唔知聽咗幾多句「光明正大使乜戴口罩」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d916b508879c44d2505a3ce13d8a04a58933452","tid":862384,"uid":145847,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8535a27c0abdde73843ad41bdb5d83125a671298","tid":862384,"uid":145847,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T19:36:37.000Z","msg":"口罩又唔比帶,野又唔講<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xS9a3tr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxS9a3tr.jpg&h=e0ec3a76&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T19:38:25.000Z","msg":"嘢又唔比講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca0a53fc5b3a29b1cc7c291cc33ba2abe8bc6cce","tid":862384,"uid":59753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T19:38:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60297347af36546fd643e0b52e812c171053ff64","tid":862384,"uid":22444,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T19:39:29.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84bc7bb5507e8f0ab0c7084f129cbeeba5775861","tid":862384,"uid":43042,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T19:42:59.000Z","msg":"其實原本成件事都冇乜野<br />\n都係叫做拉拉扯扯冇暴力<br />\n點知分開個陣無啦啦有個口罩友好似唔服氣轉身一野扑落人地個頭度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾廿部機影住<br />\n又變成左CCTVB既武器了<br />\n等睇聽日新聞點寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59c67beb382ef8188fdff4fe98724b7b7a03d4ac","tid":862384,"uid":123914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T19:43:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cfd3466e1399600d6e7821975fa7138e0a9f6c9e","tid":862384,"uid":124760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T19:44:18.000Z","msg":"邊個搶邊個咪？"},{"pid":"4458549fcccde907db9d9cf0af68c4b555566067","tid":862384,"uid":123914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T19:44:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d5a5e044776b360f94be005c01a06b99d407ce57","tid":862384,"uid":82125,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T19:49:39.000Z","msg":"香港靠班左膠撚屌飯民死撚緊，咁多年都係呃飯食，搵夠即刻退休移民，同班官一撚樣。<br />\n<br />\n奈何左膠吹雞次次都多人過本土派，呢個結唔係一時三刻可以解得開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"624437618fe64bf3a34db7e8d8731deadec84014","tid":862384,"uid":109435,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T19:52:57.000Z","msg":"同樓主一樣，睇到晒成件事<br />\n好同意個論壇搞得幾差下，唔知係發起既組織冇經驗定點，主持又麻麻地，成日都接唔到嘉賓/觀眾既說話。明明召集到一大班人去遊行，但去到公民廣場就留唔住班人，去到後段現場已經有大量空位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然佢地講既有幾個pt都幾好，但同想像中差太遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係我都打算早走既時候就出現左騷動，佢地係後面突然出現又戴晒口罩其實姚松炎嚇親唔俾咪都好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支持佢地呼籲，但咁做惹嚟反後果都好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過其他人鬧佢地戴口罩真係好無奈，又叫囂意圖蓋過佢地班聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bfc54594b295952ec510d97481444139c1a2973","tid":862384,"uid":72792,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"00b7c5734f2416d1000bd68bc7cdcf8de75a051b","tid":862384,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{